      "name": "❓ Dark FAQ — 6 Questions",
      "desc": "Accordion FAQ with dark bg — covers trial, cancellation, security, and billing",
      "sectionType": "faq",
      "props": {
        "heading": "Questions? We've Got Answers.",
        "subheading": "If you don't find what you're looking for, our team typically replies within 2 hours.",
        "q1": "Do I need a credit card to start?",
        "a1": "No. Your free plan is free forever — no credit card required. You only enter payment details when you choose to upgrade to a paid plan.",
        "q2": "How does the 14-day trial work?",
        "a2": "When you upgrade, you get 14 days free with full access to all Pro features. If you're not 100% satisfied, cancel before day 14 and you won't be charged — guaranteed.",
        "q3": "Can I export my website if I leave?",
        "a3": "Absolutely. You own your content. Export everything as clean, production-ready HTML, React components, or a JSON backup — any time, with one click.",
        "q4": "Is my data secure?",
        "a4": "Yes. We use AES-256 encryption, daily automated backups, and are SOC 2 Type II certified. Your data is hosted on geo-redundant servers with 99.99% uptime SLA.",
        "q5": "Do you offer discounts for startups or non-profits?",
        "a5": "Yes — we offer 50% off for verified startups (under 2 years, under $1M ARR) and non-profit organisations. Reach out to our team with verification and we'll sort it within 24 hours.",
        "q6": "What happens if I hit my plan limits?",
        "a6": "We'll notify you at 80% usage and again at 100%. You'll never be hard-blocked — we give you a 7-day grace period to upgrade before any restrictions apply.",
